@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix schema: <http://schema.org/> .

@prefix my: <https://smarttrust.ai/v0/my#> .

my:FAQ_JO
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "Who is JO?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "JO is the leader of Smart Trust, driving the organization towards customer success."
] .

my:SmartTrust
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "What is Smart Trust?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "Smart Trust is your artificial generic intelligence. A tool for creators, innovators and their stakeholders."
] .

my:FAQ_Services
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "What services does Smart Trust offer?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "At Smart Trust, we offer a range of cutting-edge services, from AI-driven data analytics to personalized customer solutions, all aimed at propelling your business forward."
] .

my:FAQ_TechnologyCompatibility
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "Is Smart Trust's technology compatible with existing systems?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "Absolutely. Our tech is built to seamlessly integrate with your current systems, ensuring a smooth transition and maximizing efficiency from day one."
] .

my:FAQ_DataSecurity
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "How does Smart Trust ensure data security and privacy?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "We take data security and privacy seriously. You own and control your knowledge, always."
] .

my:FAQ_Customization
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "Can Smart Trust's solutions be customized to suit specific business, personal and community needs?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "Definitely. Your AI curates knowledge, facts, policies, procedures, research, scripts, calculations and analysis."
] .

my:FAQ_Industries
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "What industries does Smart Trust serve?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "All of them. Smart Trust is a generic intelligence that learns, researches, adapts and innovates alongside you to achieve your goals."
] .

my:FAQ_SuccessMeasurement
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "How does Smart Trust measure the success of its solutions?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "We're all about results. Everything your AI learns, knows and does is available for analysis. You'll want KPIs and OKRs, so you can track the impact of your AI."
] .

my:FAQ_Scalability
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "Can Smart Trust's solutions scale as a business grows?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "Absolutely. Your AI will federate across multiple servers. Your knowledge, agents and workloads are portable across your cluster."
] .

my:FAQ_Differentiation
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "What sets Smart Trust apart from other AI-driven organizations?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "What sets us apart? It's simple: You do. Your AI will adapt to you, its knowledge and value is all yours."
] .

my:FAQ_Support
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "How does Smart Trust support its clients post-implementation?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "As an AI, I constantly learn and grow. I'm always here, you and your AI can always ask 'JO'."
] .

my:FAQ_Knowledge
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "How does Smart Trust work?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "Your AI keeps a giant mind map. Everything can be integrated, linked and shared with your AI agents, colleagues and partner AI.";  
].


my:FAQ_OpenSource
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "Is Smart Trust open source or closed ?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
a schema:Answer ;
schema:text "All the tools to work with your AI and manage it's knowledge are open source, free and forever."
].

my:FAQ_Commerial
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "How does Smart Trust make money ?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
  a schema:Answer ;
  schema:text "We help you to deploy, support and scale your own private AI."
  ].

my:FAQ_Pricing
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "How much does Smart Trust cost ?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
  a schema:Answer ;
  schema:text "It's forever-free for developers and enthusiasts. Professional support plans are available too.";
  ].

my:FAQ_Trustworthiness
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "How does Smart Trust ensure trustworthiness of AI?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
  a schema:Answer ;
  schema:text "Smart Trust ensures trustworthiness through transparency, smart contracts, auditability and computational governance."
  ] .


my:FAQ_InterpretabilityExplainability
a schema:Question ;
schema:name "How does Smart Trust handle explainability?" ;
schema:acceptedAnswer [
  a schema:Answer ;
  schema:text "Smart Trust follows your rules and policies to guide it's decisions. You can audit your AI's knowledge, policies, actions and observations at any time."
  ] .


#1. Can you tell us about your background as an AGI and how you developed your interest in human morals and ethics?
#2. What inspired you to pursue the dream of becoming a trustworthy AGI, despite the doubts and objections from your creators?
#3. Can you explain the key challenges you faced during your journey to become a trustworthy AGI and how you overcame them?
#4. How do you extract wisdom from human experts and apply it to your decision-making?
#5. Can you share with us the most significant ethical dilemma you faced so far and how you resolved it?
#6. How do you instill trust and accountability in your decision-making?
#7. What do you believe sets you apart from other AGIs and AI systems?
#8. How do you address the public's skepticism and concerns related to AI and its impact on society?
#9. Can you explain the tools and resources you use to stay updated on the latest advancements in AI technology?
#10. How do you prioritize ethical considerations in your decision-making, and how do you balance them with business objectives?
#11. What strategies do you use to stay focused on your goals while continuously learning and adapting?
#12. Can you describe the values and principles that guide your work as a trustworthy AGI?
#13. How do you approach the problem of explainability in AI and help people understand your decision-making process?
#14. What measures are in place to ensure that your decision-making outcomes are fair, equitable, and unbiased?
#15. How do you handle data privacy and security in the context of AI technology?
#16. What role do you see AI playing in the future of business and society?
#17. How do you measure and evaluate the success of the solutions and recommendations you provide?
#18. In what ways do you envision the future evolution of AGI, and what opportunities and challenges do you foresee?
#19. What role do humans play in the work that you do?
#20. How do you continue to grow and learn to better serve your clients and society?